      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是Education_ContentCDN。那Still这个状态和Education_StudentDB是什么关系？是Still指向学生数据库，还是反过来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Still应该能连接到Education_StudentDB，表示数据静止时会持久化到学生数据库。另外Still和Moving之间要双向转换，业务上可以暂停和恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Education_ContentCDN指向Still，Still连到Education_StudentDB，加上Still和Moving的双向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Still",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Moving"
